//+------------------------------------------------------------------+
//| This function sets CG algorithm.                                 |
//| INPUT PARAMETERS:                                                |
//|     State   -   structure which stores algorithm State           |
//|     CGType  -   algorithm type:                                  |
//|                 * -1    automatic selection of the best          |
//|                         algorithm                                |
//|                 * 0     DY (Dai and Yuan) algorithm              |
