//|     min(0.5*(x-x_origin)'*A*(x-x_origin)+b'*(x-x_origin))        |
//| INPUT PARAMETERS:                                                |
//|     State   -   structure which stores algorithm State           |
//|     XOrigin -   origin, array[N].                                |
